s%20and%20Epic%20Games%20has%20long%20sought%20to%20have%20payments%20for%20its%20mobile%20games%20take%20place%20outside%20the%20Google%20or%20Apple%20app%20stores%20that%20take%20a%20big%20commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEpic%20had%20mostly%20lost%20its%20similar%20case%20against%20Apple%2C%20where%20a%20US%20judge%20mostly%20ruled%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20iPhone%20maker.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20and%20Google%20regularly%20argue%20that%20their%20app%20shop%20commissions%20are%20industry-standard%20and%20that%20they%20pay%20for%20benefits%20such%20as%20reach%2C%20transaction%20security%2C%20and%20ferreting%20out%20malware.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle%20is%20also%20defending%20itself%20in%20federal%20court%20in%20Washington%2C%20where%20Justice%20Department%20officials%20accuse%20the%20company%20of%20acting%20illegally%20to%20preserve%20the%20dominance%20of%20its%20world-leading%20search%20engine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20case%20by%20the%20department%20is%20Google's%20massive%20revenue%20sharing%20deals%20in%20which%20iPhone%20maker%20Apple%20takes%20a%20big%20cut%20of%20Google%20ad%20revenue%20made%20from%20being%20the%20default%20search%20engine%20on%20Apple%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702355580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fla7jemko_epic-games-generic-reuters_625x300_28_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Falphabet-loses-antitrust-fight-with-epic-games-over-google-play-4657934%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Epic%20Games%2C%20the%20maker%20of%20Fortnite%2C%20won%20a%20major%20US%20court%20battle%20against%20Google%20on%20Monday%20when%20a%20jury%20decided%20that%20the%20search%20engine%20giant%20wields%20illegal%20monopoly%20power%20through%20its%20Android%20