%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20Army%20developed%20a%20%26quot%3Bfortress%20strategy%26quot%3B%20to%20defend%20Dacca%20(now%20Dhaka)%20during%20the%201971%20Bangladesh%20Liberation%20War.%20The%20East%20Pakistan%20army%20planned%20to%20create%20a%20fortress-like%20formation%20in%20cities%20around%20Dacca%20and%20then%20fall%20back%20to%20the%20capital%20when%20these%20%26quot%3Bfortresses%26quot%3B%20fell.%20Fifty-two%20years%20ago%2C%20on%20December%2011-12%2C%20the%20Indian%20Army%20outmanoeuvred%20the%20retreating%20Pakistani%20troops%20with%20an%20airborne%20operation%20to%20march%20forward%20towards%20Dhaka.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhaka%20is%20between%20the%20Padma%20River%20on%20its%20west%20and%20Meghna%20on%20its%20east.%20The%20Indian%20Army's%202%20and%2033%20Corps%20quickly%20marched%20deep%20into%20Bangladesh%20in%20districts%20west%20of%20the%20Jamna-Padma%20river.%20The%20Tezpur-based%204%20corps%20started%20operations%20to%20cross%20the%20Meghna%20and%20finally%20enter%20Dhaka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBehind%20Enemy%20Lines%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20army%20started%20retreating%20towards%20Dhaka%20after%20the%20%26quot%3Bfortresses%26quot%3B%20started%20falling.%20The%20Indian%20Army%20outfoxed%20Pakistan%20with%20a%20battalion-sized%20airborne%20operation%20to%20take%20on%20a%20brigade%20that%20would%20eventually%20become%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20Lt%20Gen%20AAK%20Niazi%2C%20the%20commander%20of%20the%20East%20Pakistan%20army%2C%20to%20surrender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan's%2093%20Infantry%20Brigade%20started%20retreating%20from%20Jamalpur%20and%20Mymensingh%2C%20located%20north%20of%20Dhaka.%20The%20Indian%20Army%20did%20the%20unthinkable.%202%20Para%20or%202nd%20Battalion%20of%20the%20Parachute%20regiment%20was%20airlifted%20from%20the%20Kalaikunda%20and%20Dum%20Dum%20bases%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20were%20para-dropped%20near%20Tangail%2C%20approximately%2085%20northwest%20of%20Dhaka%2C%20to%20capture%20the%20Poongli%20bridge%20on%20the%20Jamalpur-Tangail%20road%20and%20secure%20the%20ferry%20site%20over%20the%20Lohaganj%20river%20and%20intercept%20the%2093%20Infantry%20Brigade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F2pvokbmg_iaf-tangail-_625x300_12_December_23.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20established%20air%20superiority%20in%20east%20Pakistan%2C%20making%20airborne%20operations%20like%20Tangail%20possible.%20Around%20750%20paratroopers%20of%202%20Para%20under%20the%20command%20of%20Lt%20Col%20Kulwant%20Singh%20Pannu%2C%20aboard%206%20An-12s%2C%2020%20Fairchild%20Packets%20and%2022%20Dakota%20aircraft%20were%20airborne%20for%20the%20mission%20with%20Gnats%20and%20Mig-21%20providing%20air%20defence.%20The%20drop%20zone%20was%20located%20east%20of%20the%20Poongli%20bridge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F6bhk3krg_tangail-1971_625x300_12_December_23.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tangail%20airdrop%20was%20not%20a%20mission%20planned%20during%20the%20war%20but%20weeks%20before%20the%20official%20declaration.%20Indian%20Army%20Officer%20Captain%20PK%20Ghosh%20penetrated%20enemy%20lines%20in%20November%20to%20link%20up%20the%20Mukti%20Bahini's%20commander%20Kader%20Siddiqui%20and%20mark%20the%20drop%20zone%20for%20the%20airborne%20operation.%20It%20was%20the%20largest%20airborne%20operation%20since%20World%20War%202%20and%20the%20first%20in%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%204%3A30%20pm%20on%20December%2011%2C%20around%20750%20paratroopers%20airborne%20from%20Kalaikunda%20and%20Dum%20Dum%20were%20dropped.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Battle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2%20Para%20successfully%20captured%20the%20ferry%20site%20held%20by%20Pakistan's%20two%20platoon-sized%20groups.%20The%20Pakistani%20troops%2C%20withdrawing%20towards%20Tangail%2C%20attacked%20the%20Poongli%20bridge%20but%20it%20was%20countered%20successfully%20by%202%20Para.%20A%20wave%20of%20battalion-sized%20attacks%20from%20the%20flanks%20was%20carried%20out%20by%20Pakistan%20in%20which%20143%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20in%20action%20and%20two%20of%20their%20officers%20along%20with%2029%20soldiers%2C%20were%20captured.%20The%202%20Para%20suffered%20three%20casualties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20morning%20on%20December%2012%2C%20Pakistan%20launched%20two%20more%20attacks%20that%20were%20repulsed%20by%202%20Para%2C%20with%20Pakistani%20troops%20suffering%20over%20100%20casualties.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20an%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20air%20strike%20during%20the%20day%20and%20the%2093%20Infantry%20Brigade%20(approximately%202%2C000-3%2C000%20men)%20ceased%20to%20exist.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EInformation%20Warfare%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELt%20Col%20(later%20Major%20General)%20Kulwant%20Singh%20Pannu%20was%20awarded%20the%20Maha%20Vir%20Chakra.%202%20Para%20was%20the%20first%20unit%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20to%20reach%20Dacca%20after%20linking%20up%20with%201%20Mahar%20and%20entering%20Lt%20Gen%20Niazi's%20office%20in%20the%20capital%20city.%20Ram%20Mohan%20Rao%2C%20the%20then%20Public%20Relations%20Officer%20(PRO)%20of%20the%20army%2C%20decided%20to%20use%20the%20operation%20for%20information%20warfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENewspapers%20were%20informed%20about%20the%20mission%20but%20no%20photo%20of%20the%20paradrop%20was%20present%20since%20no%20access%20was%20available.%20Ram%20Mohan%20Rao%20shared%20a%20picture%20he%20clicked%20a%20year%20ago%20in%20Agra%20when%2050%20Para%20Brigade%20(approximately%203%2C000%20men)%20paradropped%20for%20an%20exercise%2C%20reports%20Nitin%20Gokhale%20from%20StratNews%20Global.%20Seeing%203%2C000%20men%20in%20the%20photo%20paradropping%20over%20Tangail%20brought%20fear%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20the%20Pakistani%20army%20in%20the%20east%20and%20made%20the%20Tangail%20operation%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20behind%20the%20surrender.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702355220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F6eorbhuo_tangail-mission_625x300_12_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbattle-of-tangail-when-indian-armys-paratroopers-outfoxed-pak-to-seal-dhakas-fate-in-1971-bangladesh-war-1971-4657593%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fifty-two%20years%20ago%2C%20on%20December%2011-12%2C%20the%20Indian%20Army%20outmanoeuvred%20the%20retreating%20Pakistani%20troops%20with%20an%20airborne%20operation%20to%20march%20forward%20towards%20Dhaka.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbattle-of-tangail-when-indian-armys-paratroopers-outfoxed-pak-to-seal-dhakas-fate-in-1971-bangladesh-war-1971-4657593%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbattle-of-tangail-when-indian-armys-paratroopers-outfoxed-pak-to-seal-dhakas-fate-in-1971-bangladesh-war-1971-4657593%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbattle-of-tangail-when-indian-armys-paratroopers-outfoxed-pak-to-seal-dhakas-fate-in-1971-bangladesh-war-1971-4657593%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Union%20Govt%20to%20Re-Introduce%203%20Criminal%20Law%20Bills%20Today%20After%20Making%20Changes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25203412%2FScreenshot-2023-07-25-at-8.33.25-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Union%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20withdraw%20the%20three%20new%20criminal%20law%20Bills%20that%20had%20been%20introduced%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20August.%20This%20Bills%20had%20been%20referred%20to%20the%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Home%20Affairs%20on%20August%2018%20for%20consideration.%20The%20Bills%20have%20now%20been%20withdrawn%20in%20order%20to%20incorporate%20some%20of%20the%20recommendations%20made%20by%20the%20parliamentary%20panel%2C%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fgovt-seeks-to-withdraw-3-bills-on-criminal-laws-plans-to-introduce-them-afresh%2F1882131%2F%5C%22%3Ehas%20told%20the%20House%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20parliamentary%20affairs%20minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fani%2Fstatus%2F1734443637692616870%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20reworked%20Bills%20would%20be%20introduced%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20Bills%20are%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20Bill%2C%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20Adhiniyam%20Bill%20and%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20Bill%2C%20meant%20to%20replace%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%20and%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fgovt-decides-to-withdraw-three-criminal-law-bills-9064186%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20parliamentary%20panel%2C%20headed%20by%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MP%20Brij%20Lal%2C%20had%20said%20that%20the%20government%20should%20bring%20back%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9Cunsound%20mind%E2%80%9D%20instead%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmental%20illness%E2%80%9D%2C%20since%20the%20latter%20is%20%E2%80%9Ctoo%20wide%20in%20its%20import%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20committee%20has%20accordingly%20recommended%20that%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98mental%20illness%E2%80%99%20in%20this%20Sanhita%20may%20be%20changed%20to%20%E2%80%98unsound%20mind%E2%80%99%20wherever%20it%20occurs%2C%20as%20the%20present%20one%20can%20create%20problems%20during%20the%20trial%20stage%2C%20as%20an%20accused%20person%20can%20simply%20show%20that%20he%20was%20under%20the%20influence%20of%20alcohol%20or%20drugs%20during%20the%20time%20of%20the%20commission%20of%20a%20crime%20and%20cannot%20be%20prosecuted%20even%20if%20he%20has%20committed%20the%20crime%20without%20intoxication%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20panel%E2%80%99s%20report%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fgovernment%2Fparliamentary-panel-gender-neutrality-section-377-criminalising-adultery%2Famp%5C%22%3Ehad%20stated%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20new%20Bill%20should%20still%20contain%20a%20section%20criminalising%20adultery%20%E2%80%93%20an%20act%20which%20had%20been%20decriminalised%20in%202018%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20However%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20government%20has%20not%20accepted%20this%20recommendation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20have%20been%20concerned%20about%20the%20new%20Bills%20and%20the%20changes%20they%20will%20bring%20into%20India%E2%80%99s%20justice%20system.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fthe-three-criminal-law-bills-using-criminal-law-to-establish-permanent-extra-constitutional-emergency-powers%5C%22%3EWriting%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20advocate%20and%20legal%20academic%20G.%20Mohan%20Gopal%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CTwelve%20changes%20to%20criminal%20law%20in%20the%20three%20Bills%20introduced%20in%20parliament%20in%20August%2C%202023%20will%20create%20a%20quantum%20leap%20in%20the%20power%20of%20the%20government%2C%20if%20and%20when%20it%20so%20wishes%2C%20to%20silence%20dissent%20and%20opposition%20and%20shut%20down%20public%20discourse%2C%20choking%20all%20channels%20that%20communicate%20conflicting%20news%20or%20views%20to%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702355216000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25203412%2FScreenshot-2023-07-25-at-8.33.25-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Funion-govt-withdraws-3-criminal-law-bills-to-make-changes-recommended-by-parl-panel%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bills%20were%20withdrawn%20in%20order%20to%20incorporate%20some%20of%20the%20recommendations%20made%20by%20the%20parliamentary%20panel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Funion-govt-withdraws-3-criminal-law-bills-to-make-changes-recommended-by-parl-panel%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20says%20it%20downed%20Ukraine-launched%20missile%20over%20Belgorod%20region%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702355115000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105920270%2Cimgsize-1710551.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-says-it-downed-ukraine-launched-missile-over-belgorod-region%2Farticleshow%2F105920245.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105920245.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-says-it-downed-ukraine-launched-missile-over-belgorod-region%2Farticleshow%2F105920245.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pic%3A%20Anushka%20calls%20Virat%20her%20'numero%20uno'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%