2content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20president%20Pranab%20Mukherjee's%20daughter%20Sharmishtha%20Mukherjee%20has%20said%20her%20father%20felt%20he%20was%20not%20included%20in%20the%20cabinet%20of%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20due%20to%20his%20%26quot%3Bnon-subservient%26quot%3B%20attitude.%C2%A0%20At%20the%20launch%20of%20her%20book%20%26quot%3BPranab%20My%20Father%3A%20A%20Daughter%20Remembers%26quot%3B%20on%20Monday%2C%20Sharmishtha%20said%20her%20father%20would%20say%20that%20his%20stint%20with%20former%20prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bgolden%20period%26quot%3B%20of%20his%20political%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%2C%20that%20has%20references%20taken%20from%20Pranab%20Mukherjee's%20diaries%2C%20was%20launched%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20his%20birth%20anniversary.%20The%20event%20also%20saw%20the%20attendance%20of%20Congress%20leader%20P%20Chidambaram%20and%20BJP%20leader%20Vijay%20Goel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20touched%20upon%20his%20assessment%20of%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20book%20and%20excerpts%20of%20which%20stirred%20a%20controversy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharmishtha%20said%20that%20even%20her%20father%20was%20opposed%20to%20the%20proposed%20ordinance%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20was%20torn%20by%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20September%202013%2C%20but%20he%20felt%20that%20it%20should%20be%20discussed%20in%20the%20Parliament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ordinance%20aimed%20to%20bypass%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20of%20immediate%20disqualification%20of%20convicted%20legislators%2C%20and%20instead%20proposed%20that%20they%20may%20continue%20as%20a%20member%20while%20an%20appeal%20in%20a%20higher%20court%20was%20pending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20the%20one%20to%20break%20the%20news%20(about%20tearing%20of%20the%20ordinance)%20to%20him.%20He%20was%20so%20angry%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharmishtha%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20that%20her%20father%2C%20as%20the%20President%20of%20the%20country%2C%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20worked%20as%20a%20team.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20conversation%20over%20the%20book%20with%20former%20bureaucrat%20Pavan%20K%20Varma%2C%20she%20also%20recalled%20her%20opposition%20to%20her%20father%20attending%20an%20RSS%20event.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20fought%20with%20Baba%20for%20three%20to%20four%20days%20over%20his%20decision.%20One%20day%20he%20said%20that%20it's%20not%20me%20who%20is%20giving%20legitimacy%20but%20it's%20the%20country.%20Baba%20felt%20that%20democracy%20is%20all%20about%20dialogue.%20It%20is%20about%20having%20a%20conversation%20with%20the%20opposition%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%20of%20the%20discussion%2C%20she%20had%20also%20said%20that%20the%20book%20has%20very%20few%20references%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharmishtha%20said%20that%20her%20father%20would%20often%20say%20that%20the%20Congress%20established%20parliamentary%20democracy%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bjob%20of%20upholding%20it%20lies%20with%20the%20party%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20criticism%20of%20the%20book%2C%20she%20said%20that%20none%20of%20the%20senior%20leaders%20have%20spoken%20over%20the%20book%20with%20only%20Prithviraj%20Chavan%20saying%20he%20cannot%20comment%20on%20it%20since%20he%20hasn't%20read%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20only%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20turned%20up%20among%20Congress%20leaders%2C%20Sharmishtha%20said%20that%20she%20was%20pained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20reaction%20to%20a%20certain%20excerpt%20of%20the%20book%20shows%20that%20they%20should%20introspect%20and%20see%20whether%20they%20are%20actually%20upholding%20the%20values%2C%20actually%20practising%20what%20they%20are%20preaching%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20opined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharmishtha%2C%20who%20has%20quit%20politics%2C%20also%20clarified%20that%20she%20has%20not%20tried%20to%20tweak%20her%20father's%20views%20about%20anyone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20his%20association%20with%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20father%20would%20say%20that%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20period%20was%20the%20golden%20period%20of%20his%20political%20life.%20Indiraji%20kept%20an%20eye%20on%20Baba.%20If%20there%20was%20one%20person%20with%20whom%20my%20father's%20loyalty%20lay%2C%20it%20was%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20nobody%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20how%20he%20rose%20through%20the%20ranks%20in%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20cabinet%2C%20she%20said%20it%20didn't%20happen%20in%20a%20day%20and%20underlined%20that%20the%20former%20prime%20minister%20was%20impressed%20by%20her%20father's%20homework.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20real%20bonding%20started%20post-Emergency.%20He%20stood%20by%20her%20through%20thick%20and%20thin.%20Many%20stalwarts%20left%20her%20during%20that%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20noted%2C%20while%20stressing%20that%20her%20father%20remained%20loyal%20to%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20that%20the%20imposition%20of%20Emergency%20had%20a%20historical%20context%2C%20she%20said%20that%20the%20conditions%20which%20led%20to%20it%20should%20also%20be%20looked%20into%20since%20the%20country%20was%20in%20a%20state%20of%20anarchy%20at%20that%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20made%20a%20mistake%20and%20she%20realised%20it.%20If%20I%20had%20the%20political%20maturity%2C%20a%20political%20meeting%20could%20have%20been%20managed%20between%20JP%20and%20Indira%20Gandhi...%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharmishtha%20recalled%20her%20father's%20assessment%20of%20the%20scenario%20at%20that%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20bureaucrat%20Mr%20Varma%20then%20asked%20her%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Btrust%20deficit%26quot%3B%20between%20her%20father%20and%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20succeeded%20his%20mother%20following%20her%20assassination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharmishtha%20said%20there%20were%20%26quot%3Bstories%20planted%26quot%3B%20by%20certain%20people%20that%20her%20father%20was%20not%20in%20favour%20of%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20becoming%20the%20prime%20minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20per%20Baba's%20notes%2C%20it%20was%20actually%20a%20planted%20story...to%20create%20misunderstanding%20between%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20and%20Baba.%20The%20main%20reason%20behind%20trust%20deficit%20was%20Baba's%20staunch%20personality%20and%20his%20non-subservient%20attitude.%20Baba%20said%20Rajiv%20was%20correct%20in%20not%20taking%20me%20in%20his%20cabinet%20since%20I%20am%20a%20tough%20nut%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Varma%20then%20touched%20upon%20Mukherjee%20being%20dropped%20from%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20in%20January%201986%20and%20his%20expulsion%20from%20the%20Congress%20a%20few%20months%20later%20in%20the%20same%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharmishtha%20recalled%20that%20her%20father%20was%20depressed%20and%20also%20formed%20the%20Rashtriya%20Samajwadi%20Congress%20but%20later%20returned%20to%20the%20Congress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20talked%20about%20how%20her%20father%20got%20upset%20about%20not%20being%20included%20in%20the%20PV%20Narsimha%20Rao%20cabinet%20since%20he%20considered%20the%20latter%20a%20friend%20but%20was%20offered%20the%20Planning%20Commission%20chairman's%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharmishtha%20also%20discussed%20about%20the%20working%20relationship%20between%20her%20father%20and%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Manmohan%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20exemplary%20courtesy%20shown%20by%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh...%20and%20there%20was%20a%20strong%20mutual%20respect%20between%20the%20two%20of%20them.%20They%20knew%20how%20to%20handle%20the%20differences%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukherjee%20held%20key%20portfolios%20during%20the%20Congress%20rule.%20He%20held%20charges%20of%20defence%2C%20external%20affairs%20and%20finance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Varma%20asked%20Sharmishtha%20whether%20Mukherjee%20was%20the%20first%20choice%20for%20the%20President's%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20whether%20he%20was%20the%20first%20choice%2C%20the%20second%20choice%20or%20the%20third%20choice.%20But%20from%20Baba's%20diary%2C%20I%20got%20to%20know%20that%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20was%20exploring%20the%20possibility%20and%20winnability%20of%20Shri%20Hamid%20Ansari%20ji%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702354740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F4pt8rhh_sharmishtha-mukherjee-pranab-mukherjee_625x300_12_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-pranab-mukherjee-told-daughter-sharmishtha-mukherjee-as-they-fought-about-rss-invite-4657694%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20president%20Pranab%20Mukherjee's%20daughter%20Sharmishtha%20Mukherjee%20has%20said%20her%20father%20felt%20he%20was%20not%20included%20in%20the%20cabinet%20of%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20due%20to%20his%20%26quot%3Bnon-subservient%26quot%3B%20attitude.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-pranab-mukherjee-told-daughter-sharmishtha-mukherjee-as-they-fought-about-rss-invite-4657694%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-pranab-mukherjee-told-daughter-sharmishtha-mukherjee-as-they-fought-about-rss-invite-4657694%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-pranab-mukherjee-told-daughter-sharmishtha-mukherjee-as-they-fought-about-rss-invite-4657694%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%