%20but%20that%20momentum%20has%20now%20reversed%20for%20millennials.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat's%20according%20to%20a%20November%2030%20report%20published%20by%20the%20Washington%20DC-based%20non-profit%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prb.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FLosing-More-Ground_Population-Bulletin-Vol-77-No-1.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPopulation%20Reference%20Bureau%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20studied%20the%20well-being%20of%20women%20aged%2025%20to%2034%20from%20each%20generation%20of%20Americans.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20found%20that%20women%20born%20between%201981%20and%201999%20%E2%80%94%20widely%20classified%20as%20millennials%20%E2%80%94%20have%20seen%20the%20first%20drop%20in%20well-being%20since%20the%20Silent%20Generation%20as%20they%20live%20through%20young%20adulthood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWomen%20today%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20die%20during%20their%20late%2020s%20and%20early%2030s%20than%20at%20any%20other%20point%20in%20the%20previous%20three%20generations%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMaternal%20mortality%2C%20suicide%2C%20and%20homicide%20rates%20soar%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20rate%20has%20risen%20in%20parallel%20with%20a%20startling%20increase%20in%20maternal%20mortality%20rates%20among%20women%20aged%2025%20to%2034%2C%20with%2030.4%20deaths%20due%20to%20pregnancy%20complications%20out%20of%20100%2C000%20births%20for%20millennials%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20compared%20to%2021%20deaths%20per%20100%2C000%20births%20for%20the%20Silent%20Generation%20%E2%80%94%20or%20women%20who%20were%20born%20during%20and%20before%20World%20War%20II%20%E2%80%94%20and%207.5%20for%20baby%20boomers%20and%209.2%20for%20Generation%20X%20when%20they%20were%20aged%2025%20to%2034.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20acknowledged%20that%20part%20of%20the%20surge%20might%20be%20due%20to%20better%20data%20collection%20in%20recent%20years.%20But%20it%20also%20noted%20that%20after%20all%20US%20states%20implemented%20a%20new%20data%20system%20in%202019%2C%20pregnancy%20deaths%20continued%20to%20rise%20sharply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMillennial%20women%20are%20also%20the%20first%20in%20the%20last%20century%20to%20experience%20rising%20suicide%20rates%2C%20with%207%20suicides%20among%20100%2C000%20women%20aged%2025%20to%2034%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBaby%20boomer%20and%20Gen%20X%20women%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20saw%20a%20respective%206%20and%204.4%20suicides%20per%20100%2C000%20women%20when%20they%20were%20aged%2025%20to%2034.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20White%20millennial%20women%20saw%20suicide%20rates%20decline%2C%20young%20Black%2C%20American%20Indian%20or%20Alaskan%20Native%2C%20mixed-race%2C%20and%20Hispanic%20women%20experienced%20increases.%20Statistics%20for%20women%20of%20other%20ethnicities%20were%20not%20specifically%20presented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20homicide%20rates%20for%20millennial%20women%20rose%20to%204.5%20deaths%20per%20100%2C000%20women%20aged%2025%20to%2034%2C%20compared%20to%204.3%20deaths%20for%20Gen%20X%20women%20when%20they%20were%20the%20same%20age%2C%20according%20to%20PRB.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EViolent%20deaths%20among%20young%20women%20actually%20fell%20to%203.3%20per%20100%2C000%20people%20in%202017%2C%20when%20PRB%20issued%20its%20last%20index.%20But%20statistics%20now%20show%20the%20rate%20swelled%20so%20quickly%20in%20the%20last%20six%20years%20that%20it%20surpassed%20that%20of%20Gen%20X%2C%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20with%20suicides%2C%20homicide%20rates%20are%20higher%20among%20young%20women%20of%20color%2C%20the%20report%20said.%20LGBTQ%2B%20individuals%20are%20also%20often%20targeted%20at%20far%20higher%20rates%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EContributing%20factors%20to%20the%20overall%20rise%20included%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20which%20increased%20domestic%20violence%20rates%2C%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fnumber-of-mass-shootingsin-america-this-year-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20leap%20in%20gun%20violence%20incidents%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20report%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHomicide%20is%20now%20also%20the%20leading%20cause%20of%20death%20for%20pregnant%20and%20postnatal%20women%2C%20more%20so%20than%20typical%20maternal%20mortality%20causes%2C%20the%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSadly%2C%20the%20tale%20of%20generational%20progress%20that%20we%20have%20taken%20for%20granted%20in%20recent%20generations%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20guarantee%20for%20Millennial%20and%20Gen%20Z%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report's%20authors%2C%20led%20by%20research%20analyst%20Sara%20Srygley%2C%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBut%20millennial%20women%20also%20are%20faring%20better%20in%20the%20economy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decline%20in%20safety%20among%20millennial%20women%20comes%20despite%20their%20improved%20financial%20and%20education%20status%20compared%20to%20generations%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2043.6%25%20of%20young%20millennial%20women%20in%20the%20US%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwomen-outnumber-men-in-the-college-educated-american-workforce-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egraduated%20college%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20record%20level%20in%20modern%20history.%20That's%20compared%20to%2028%25%20of%20Gen%20X%20women%20and%2022%25%20of%20baby%20boomer%20women%20who%20graduated%20by%20the%20time%20they%20turned%2034%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYoung%20millennial%20women%20are%20also%20seeing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-highest-earning-generation-less-wealthy-boomers-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereduction%20in%20the%20wage%20gap%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20earning%2089.7%20cents%20for%20every%20dollar%20that%20men%20earn%2C%20compared%20to%2082.4%20cents%20on%