Itself%20'Indian%20Air%20and%20Space%20Force'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F03173311%2FMoD-petals.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20is%20likely%20to%20imminently%20rename%20itself%20as%20the%20Indian%20Air%20and%20Space%20Force%20or%20IASF%2C%20in%20a%20move%20that%20has%20appalled%20a%20cross-section%20of%20senior%20veterans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20slew%20of%20news%20reports%20quoting%20senior%20IAF%20officials%20disclosed%20on%20December%2011%20that%20this%20re-christening%20proposal%20was%20at%20an%20%E2%80%98advanced%E2%80%99%20stage%20with%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%2C%20following%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98exhortations%E2%80%99%20at%20a%20routine%20memorial%20lecture%20last%20year%2C%20that%20the%20force%20needed%20to%20become%20an%20aerospace%20force%20to%20safeguard%20India%20from%20future%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelivering%20the%2037th%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%20P.C.%20Lal%20Memorial%20Lecture%20at%20New%20Delhi%20in%20May%202022%2C%20Singh%20had%20declared%20that%20the%20exploitation%20of%20space%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20adversaries%20for%20military%20use%2C%20would%20have%20an%20%E2%80%98adverse%E2%80%99%20effect%20and%20one%20which%20the%20country%20needed%20to%20%E2%80%98identify%20and%20be%20fully%20prepared%E2%80%99%20to%20counter.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20students%20of%20military%20affairs%20and%20geopolitics%2C%20it%20is%20our%20duty%20to%20keep%20anticipating%20the%20nature%20of%20future%20wars%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20had%20stated%2C%20adding%20that%20space%20was%20one%20area%20that%20presented%20the%20IAF%20and%20the%20military%20in%20general%2C%20an%20impending%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAF%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20its%20planned%20name%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%98%3Cstrong%3Efirman%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20official%20sources%20in%20the%20service%20said%20there%20was%20a%20%E2%80%98growing%20need%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20IAF%20to%20%E2%80%98take%20ownership%20of%20space%E2%80%99%20and%20declare%20as%20much%20in%20its%20identity.%20They%20also%20said%20that%20the%20name-change%20idea%20had%20emanated%20internally%20as%2C%20in%20an%20era%20of%20competitive%20claims%2C%20the%20IAF%20was%20anxious%20to%20better%20project%20its%20intended%20enhanced%20capabilities%20in%20the%20space%20realm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAFs%20name%20change%2C%20however%2C%20would%20be%20its%20third%20after%20its%20founding%20in%20October%201932%20by%20the%20British%20Colonial%20administration%20in%20Karachi%20as%20an%20auxiliary%20force%20of%20the%20Royal%20Air%20Force%20(RAF)%20with%20six%20officers%20and%2019%20Havai%20Sepoys%20or%20air%20soldiers.%20Thereafter%2C%20in%20recognition%20of%20its%20valiant%20service%20in%20WW2%20King%20George%20VI%20conferred%20on%20it%20the%20prefix%20Royal%E2%80%9D%20on%20March%2012%2C%201945%2C%20rendering%20it%20the%20RIAF.%20And%2C%20in%201950%2C%20when%20India%20became%20a%20republic%2C%20the%20Royal%20prefix%20was%20dropped%20and%20it%20reverted%20to%20being%20simply%20the%20IAF%20and%20has%20continued%20to%20be%20so%20for%20nearly%20four%20generations%20since%2C%20and%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20as%20a%20formidable%2C%20albeit%20familiar%20fighting%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20IAF%E2%80%99s%20top%20brass%20seem%20to%20have%20taken%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20generic%20observation%20on%20the%20military%20exploitation%20of%20space%20as%20a%20%3Cem%3Efirman%3C%2Fem%3E%20(order)%20from%20the%20government%20and%20furiously%20activated%20the%20proposal%20to%20change%20its%20name%20to%20include%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20three-star%20IAF%20veteran.%20It%E2%80%99s%20%C2%A0quite%20amazing%20the%20depths%20the%20service%20will%20plumb%20in%20order%20to%20%E2%80%98please%E2%80%99%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20political%20establishment%2C%20he%20fulminated%2C%20declining%20to%20be%20named%2C%20as%20he%20feared%20his%20pension%20payments%20would%20be%20stopped%20as%20%E2%80%98punishment%E2%80%99%20for%20airing%20adverse%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Already%20an%20aerospace%20force%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20IAF%20is%20already%20an%20aerospace%20force%2C%20and%20should%20continue%20as%20the%20IAF%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20technological%20advances%20it%20absorbs%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20defence%20analyst%20Air%20Marshal%20V.K.%20%E2%80%98Jimmy%E2%80%99%20Bhatia%2C%20one%20of%20a%20handful%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20military%20officers%20who%20agreed%20to%20be%20identified.%20But%20if%20the%20government%20or%20the%20IAF%2C%20or%20even%20both%2C%20were%20%C2%A0hell%20bent%20on%20the%20renaming%20it%20could%2C%20at%20best%2C%20be%20re-baptised%20as%20the%20Indian%20Aerospace%20Force%2C%20he%20declared.%20But%20to%20rename%20it%20as%20the%20IASF%20would%20be%20somewhat%20excessive%20and%20needless%2C%20added%20the%20IAF%E2%80%99s%20most%20decorated%20fighter%20pilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20elaborating%C2%A0excessively%C2%A0upon%20the%20IAF%E2%80%99s%20fledgling%20space-related%20capabilities%2C%20which%20were%20proliferating%20incrementally%2C%C2%A0numerous%20other%20considerations%20need%20evaluating%20with%20regard%20to%20its%20projected%20name-change.%20For%2C%20other%20than%20its%20overall%20futility%20which%2C%20in%20no%20way%2C%20would%20be%20a%20value-addition%20to%20the%20IAFs%20present%20standing%20or%20operational%20capability%2C%20was%20the%20overall%20cost%20entailed%20in%20such%20a%20makeover%20endeavour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20though%20it%20was%20admittedly%20difficult%2C%20if%20not%20impossible%20to%20assess%20this%20%E2%80%93%20and%20it%20was%20highly%20unlikely%20if%20either%20the%20MoD%20or%20even%20the%20IAF%20for%20that%20matter%2C%20had%20even%20an%20approximate%20expenditure%20in%20mind%20%E2%80%93%20it%E2%80%99s%20instructive%20to%20defer%20to%20South%20African%20intellectual%20property%20rights%20lawyer%20Darren%20Oliver%20for%20this%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20innovative%20attorney%20had%20evolved%20a%20calculative%20method%20or%20abacus%20in%202018%2C%20when%20the%20ruler%20of%20Swaziland%20decided%20to%20rename%20his%20country%20as%20Eswantini%2C%20and%20estimated%20that%20the%20expense%20incurred%20in%20such%20an%20undertaking%20would%20approximate%20over%20%2460%20million.%20Oliver%E2%80%99s%20involved%20formula%2C%20too%20convoluted%20to%20explicate%2C%20gained%20momentary%20salience%20in%20India%20recently%20during%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20September%2C%20when%20there%20was%20talk%20of%20renaming%20the%20country%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECosts%20and%20%E2%80%98mere%20declaration%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20financial%20analysts%20had%20pegged%20the%20price%20of%20this%20prospective%20name-change%20to%20Bharat%20at%20around%20Rs%2014%2C304%20crore.%20And%20whilst%20the%20price%20of%20renaming%20the%20IAF%20would%20be%20nowhere%20as%20steep%2C%20recasting%20its%20propositioned%20IASF%20moniker%2C%20and%20possibly%20even%20a%20new%20ensign%20to%20supplant%20the%20one%20unveiled%20in%20early%20October%2C%20on%20hundreds%20of%20its%20platforms%2C%20bases%20and%20innumerable%20other%20assets%20and%20properties%2C%20would%20be%20%E2%80%98considerable%E2%80%99%20in%20times%20of%20enduring%20fiscal%20penury%20and%20when%20frugality%20and%20force%20modernisation%20was%20the%20guiding%20mantra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20changes%20in%20uniform%20badges%20and%20letterheads%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20myriad%20other%20areas%2C%20would%20only%20add%20to%20the%20cost%20of%20what%20some%20veterans%20called%20a%20mere%20%E2%80%98dalliance%E2%80%99%20or%20uncalled-for%20%E2%80%98window-dressing%E2%80%99%20that%20had%20seemingly%20become%20the%20custom%20in%20the%20armed%20forces%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMerely%20declaring%20itself%20to%20be%20a%20space%20power%20does%20not%20necessarily%20make%20the%20IAF%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20former%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20official%2C%20also%20requesting%20anonymity.%20It%20has%20to%20significantly%20prove%20its%20credentials%2C%20he%20tersely%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20unnamed%20veterans%20concurred%20that%20the%20IAF%20was%20no%20commercial%20enterprise%20that%20needed%20to%20%E2%80%98rebrand%E2%80%99%20itself%20in%20order%20to%20endear%20itself%20to%20its%20principals%20or%20customers.%20One%20two-star%20officer%20even%20stated%20that%20such%20%E2%80%98marketing%20gimmicks%20were%20best%20suited%20to%20a%20business%20and%20certainly%20not%20the%20military.%20Another%20speculated%20that%20the%20IAF%E2%80%99s%20re-branding%20could%2C%20in%20future%2C%20also%20result%20in%20the%20other%20two%20services%20seeking%20a%20name%20change%20as%20their%20future%20operational%20capabilities%20burgeoned%20into%20newer%20sphere%20with%20advanced%20in%20technology.%20There%20was%20no%20end%20to%20such%20absurdity%2C%20he%20remonstrated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuccessive%20Air%20Chief%20Marshals%20had%2C%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20IAF%20developing%20offensive%20and%20defensive%20space%20capabilities%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20token%20tri-service%20Defence%20Space%20Agency%20(DSA)%20in%202019%20headquartered%20in%20Bangalore%2C%20that%20also%C2%A0incorporated%C2%A0within%20itself%20the%C2%A0Defence%20Imagery%20Processing%20and%20Analysis%20Centre%20in%C2%A0Delhi%20and%20the%20Defence%20Satellite%20Control%20Centre%20in%C2%A0Bhopal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20seminar%20in%20Delhi%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%20V.R.%20Chaudhuri%20declared%20that%20defence%20minister%20Singh%20had%20%E2%80%98categorically%20stated%E2%80%99%20that%20it%20was%20time%20for%20the%20IAF%20to%20become%20an%20%E2%80%98aerospace%20power%E2%80%99%20And%2C%20with%20%E2%80%98on-demand%20launch%E2%80%99%20of%20satellites%20and%20spacecraft%20by%20private%20and%20military%20stakeholders%20becoming%20the%20norm%2C%20space%20had%20emerged%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98ultimate%20high%20ground%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20IAF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20the%20IAF%20had%20opted%20to%20take%20the%20path%20of%20least%20development%20via%20plans%20to%20first%20proclaim%20itself%20a%20space%20power%20through%20a%20name-change%2C%20and%20then%20to%20secure%20that%20capability.%20The%20IAF%20appears%20to%20be%20simply%20playing%20at%20being%20aspiring%20boastful%20achievers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702351921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F03173311%2FMoD-petals.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Findian-air-force-space-rename-rajnath-singh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'The%20IAF%E2%80%99s%20top%20brass%20seem%20to%20have%20taken%20Rajnath%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20generic%20observation%20on%20the%20military%20exploitation%20of%20space%20as%20an%20order%20from%20the%20government...'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Findian-air-force-space-rename-rajnath-singh%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IPL%202024%20Auction%3A%20Who%20Are%20The%203%20Indians%20In%20INR%202%20Crore%20Price%20Bracket%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024%20auction%20player%20list%20has%20been%20released%2C%20with%20a%20total%20of%20333%20players%20set%20to%20go%20under%20the%20hammer.%20The%20auction%2C%20which%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Dubai%20on%20December%2019%2C%20will%20see%20only%20three%20Indian%20players'%20names%20being%20brought%20up%20in%20the%20INR%202%20crore%20price%20bracket.%20There%20isn't%20any%20Indian%20player%20in%20the%20INR%201.5%20crore%20and%20INR%201%20