n%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702336849000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2FScreen-Shot-2023-12-11-at-1.09.07-PM.png%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235833435%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anne%20Hathaway%20appeared%20on%20the%20latest%20%E2%80%9CHappy%20Sad%20Confused%E2%80%9D%20podcast%20and%20called%20it%20%E2%80%9Clucky%E2%80%9D%20that%20her%20iteration%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CBarbie%E2%80%9D%20movie%20never%20got%20off%20the%20ground%20considering%20the%20phenomenon%20that%20Margot%20Robbie%20and%20Greta%20Gerwig%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CBarbie%E2%80%9D%20became%20over%20the%20summer.%20Back%20in%20July%202017%2C%20Hathaway%20was%20announced%20as%20the%20star%20of%20Sony%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CBarbie%E2%80%9D%20movie.%20Comedian%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Zack%20Sharf%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fanne-hathaway-barbie-never-made-lucky-1235833435%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fanne-hathaway-barbie-never-made-lucky-1235833435%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fanne-hathaway-barbie-never-made-lucky-1235833435%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22People%20lost%20nearly%2050%20pounds%20on%20Zepbound%20%E2%80%94%20but%20gained%20more%20than%20half%20back%20when%20they%20stopped%20taking%20it%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222116%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20close-up%20weight%20scale%20with%20a%20doctor%20adjusting%20the%20balance%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657765547a3c8094d5dbc252%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221416%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETirzepatide%20and%20similar%20medications%20can%20lead%20to%20significant%20weight%20loss%2C%20but%20evidence%20suggests%20you%20need%20to%20stay%20on%20the%20drugs%20long-term%20to%20maintain%20it.%3Cp%3EPeter%20Dazeley%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETirzepatide%2C%20a%20drug%20newly%20approved%20to%20treat%20obesity%2C%20helped%20people%20lose%2020%25%20of%20body%20weight%20on%20average.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20growing%20evidence%20suggests%20patients%20need%20to%20keep%20taking%20the%20drug%20to%20maintain%20the%20results.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPeople%20who%20stopped%20taking%20the%20drug%20regained%20more%20than%20half%20what%20they%20lost%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20study.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20even%20more%20evidence%20that%20a%20wildly%20popular%20medication%20can%20help%20people%20lose%20significant%20weight%20and%20keep%20it%20off%20%E2%80%94%20but%20only%20if%20they%20continue%20taking%20the%20drug.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ftirzepatide-weight-loss-drug-vs-semaglutide-glp-1-agonist-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETirzepatide%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20once-weekly%20injection%2C%20is%20part%20of%20a%20group%20of%20medications%20that%20work%20by%20acting%20on%20a%20hormone%20called%20GLP-1%20to%20help%20regulate%20appetite%20and%20blood%20sugar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drug%20has%20been%20available%20for%20diabetes%20treatment%20since%202022%2C%20sold%20under%20the%20brand%20name%20Mounjaro%2C%20.%20It%20was%20FDA-approved%20specifically%20for%20weight%20management%20in%20November%20of%20this%20year%20under%20the%20brand%20name%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Feli-lilly-mounjaro-zepbound-approved-weight-loss-stronger-than-wegovy-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZepbound%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20taking%20tirzepatide%20lost%20an%20average%20of%20nearly%2050%20pounds%20in%20less%20than%20a%20year%2C%20but%20gained%20more%20than%20half%20of%20it%20back%20if%20they%20stopped%20taking%20the%20drug%2C%20according%20to%20a%20study%20published%20December%2011%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjama%2Ffullarticle%2F2812936%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJAMA%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20researchers%20from%20several%20universities%2C%20including%20Weill%20Cornell%20Medicine%2C%20looked%20at%20670%20people%20on%20tirzepatide%20as%20part%20of%20a%20clinical%20trial%20funded%20by%20the%20drug's%20manufacturer%2C%20pharmaceutical%20company%20Eli%20Lilly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20participants%20took%20tirzepatide%20for%2036%20weeks%2C%20during%20which%20they%20lost%20an%20average%20of%2020%25%20of%20their%20body%20weight%20(roughly%2046%20pounds).%20Then%2C%20one%20group%20of%20patients%20was%20randomly%20assigned%20to%20a%20placebo%20instead%20of%20continuing%20the%20medication%20for%20the%20next%2052%20weeks.%20The%20patients%20in%20the%20other%20group%20were%20assigned%20to%20continue%20taking%20the%20drug%20during%20this%20time%20(although%20not%20all%20of%20the%20patients%20in%20either%20group%20completed%20the%20study%2C%20often%20for%20reasons%20unrelated%20to%20the%20medication).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20found%20that%20people%20who%20stopped%20taking%20tirzepatide%20regained%20about%2014%25%20of%20their%20body%20weight%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20half%20of%20what%20they%20had%20initially%20lost%20%E2%80%94%20over%20the%20year%20of%20follow-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20group%20who%20kept%20taking%20the%20drug%20not%20only%20maintained%20their%20results%2C%20but%20went%20on%20to%20lose%20even%20more%20weight%20(an%20additional%205.5%25%20of%20their%20body%20weight%2C%20on%20average)%20over%2052%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20placebo%20group%20still%20ended%20up%20lighter%20than%20they%20had%20been%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20study%2C%20the%20results%20add%20to%20existing%20evidence%20that%20tirzepatide%20and%20similar%20drugs%20only%20work%20as%20long%20as%20patients%20keep%20taking%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESemaglutide%2C%20sold%20as%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy%2C%20works%20the%20same%20way%2C%20as%20patients%20who%20stopped%20taking%20the%20drug%20regained%20about%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20weight%20they%20had%20lost%2C%20according%20to%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F35441470%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20also%20underscore%20what%20doctors%20have%20previously%20known%20about%20these%20medications%3A%20patients%20need%20to%20take%20them%20long-term%2C%20and%20possibly%20for%20life%2C%20to%20maintain%20the%20health%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20phenomenon%20isn't%20unique%20to%20drugs%20used%20for%20weight%20management.%20Many%20common%20medications%20need%20to%20be%20taken%20continuously%20in%20order%20to%20help%20treat%20chronic%20conditions%20such%20as%20hypertension%2C%20diabetes%2C%20or%20high%20cholesterol.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20doctors%20have%20previously%20said%20that%20patients%20can%20face%20major%20obstacles%20if%20staying%20on%20the%20medications%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESides%20effects%2C%20shortages%2C%20and%20a%20high%20price%20tag%20can%20make%20weight%20loss%20drugs%20difficult%20to%20take%20long-term%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20research%20suggests%20that%20as%20many%20as%20two-thirds%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fmost-patients-stop-weight-loss-drugs-wegovy-after-one-year-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeople%20on%20weight%20loss%20drugs%20stop%20taking%20them%20within%20a%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFactors%20like%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20drugs%2C%20ability%20to%20get%20them%2C%20and%20unwanted%20effects%20can%20all%20play%20role%20in%20people%20opting%20to%20discontinue%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20tirzepatide%20is%20considered%20safe%2C%20it%20does%20have%20well-documented%20side%20effects%2C%20typically%20mild%20to%20moderate%20gastrointestinal%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E