%2C%22published%22%3A1702297069000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105906703%2Cimgsize-72796.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Faustralia-to-tighten-visa-rules-for-students-workers-in-a-bid-to-halve-migrant-intake%2Farticleshow%2F105906523.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105906523.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20Australian%20government%20announced%20a%20crackdown%20on%20the%20migration%20system%20in%20Australia%20by%20tightening%20visa%20rules%20for%20low-skilled%20workers%20and%20international%20students.%20They%20introduced%20a%2010-year%20migration%20strategy.%20The%20new%20rules%20include%20higher%20English%20test%20ratings%20for%20international%20students%20and%20increased%20scrutiny%20on%20second%20visa%20applications.%20The%20government%20aims%20to%20raise%20living%20standards%2C%20improve%20working%20conditions%2C%20and%20strengthen%20international%20relationships.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Faustralia-to-tighten-visa-rules-for-students-workers-in-a-bid-to-halve-migrant-intake%2Farticleshow%2F105906523.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Since%202015%2C%2065.9%25%20of%20118%20Lakh%20Commissioned%20Houses%20Completed%20Under%20PMAY-U%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26191526%2F1280px-View_of_Lok_Sabha_chamber_in_the_New_Parliament_building_New_Delhi.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20total%20of%2065.9%25%20of%20houses%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Awas%20Yojana-Urban%20(PMAY-U)%20have%20been%20completed%20and%20delivered%20to%20beneficiaries%20since%20the%20scheme%E2%80%99s%20inception%20in%202015%20until%20December%204.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20flagship%20scheme%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20seeks%20to%20provide%20housing%20for%20all%20to%20the%20urban%20poor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20written%20reply%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Monday%2C%20minister%20of%20state%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Housing%20and%20Urban%20Affairs%20Kaushal%20Kishore%20said%20that%20PMAY-U%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdemand-driven%20scheme%20and%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20not%20fixed%20any%20target%20for%20construction%20of%20houses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20scheme%20has%20been%20implemented%20under%20the%20%E2%80%9CHousing%20for%20All%E2%80%9D%20Mission%20since%20June%202015%20to%20provide%20Central%20assistance%20to%20implementing%20agencies%20through%20states%20and%20Union%20Territories%20(UTs)%20for%20providing%20all-weather%20pucca%20houses%20with%20basic%20civic%20services%20to%20all%20eligible%20urban%20beneficiaries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20figures%20given%20by%20Kishore%20in%20his%20reply%201%2C18%2C63%2C073%20have%20been%20sanctioned%2C%201%2C13%2C42%2C815%20have%20been%20grounded%20and%2078%2C26%2C765%20have%20been%20completed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPMAY-U%20is%20a%20demand%20driven%20scheme%20and%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20not%20fixed%20any%20target%20for%20construction%20of%20houses.%20Based%20on%20the%20project%20proposals%20submitted%20by%20States%2F%20UTs%2C%20as%20on%2004.12.2023%2C%20118.63%20lakh%20houses%20have%20been%20sanctioned%20under%20PMAY-U%2C%20out%20of%20which%20113.43%20lakh%20have%20been%20grounded%20for%20construction%3B%20of%20which%2078.27%20lakh%20have%20been%20completed%2F%20delivered%20to%20beneficiaries%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kishore%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKishore%20said%20that%20the%20timeline%20for%20completion%20of%20projects%20varies%20from%20state%20to%20state%20and%20generally%20takes%20around%2012%20to%2036%20months.%20The%20scheme%20period%20which%20had%20earlier%20set%20a%20deadline%20of%20March%202022%20has%20been%20extended%20up%20to%20December%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20provided%20figures%20for%20the%20houses%20sanctioned%20under%20the%20scheme%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202020-21%20a%20total%20of%2016%2C81%2C038%20houses%20were%20sanctioned%2C%2018%2C14%2C606%20in%202021-22%20and%2010%2C01%2C739%20in%202022-23.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20monsoon%20session%20in%20July%20this%20year%2C%20minister%20for%20housing%20and%20urban%20affairs%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Puri%20told%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%20a%20written%20reply%20that%20a%20total%20of%2075.51%20lakh%20houses%20have%20been%20completed%20%E2%80%93%20out%20of%20which%2071.39%20lakh%20have%20been%20occupied%2C%20reported%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fparliament-proceedings-7551-lakh-houses-completed-under-pmay-u%2Farticle67142907.ece%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20had%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20houses%20completed%20at%2012%2C87%2C307%2C%20while%20Gujarat%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20were%20the%20other%20high-performing%20states%20with%208%2C80%2C209%20and%208%2C08%2C278%20houses%20completed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702296950000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26191526%2F1280px-View_of_Lok_Sabha_chamber_in_the_New_Parliament_building_New_Delhi.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpmay-u-66-percent-houses-completed-lok-sabha%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20written%20reply%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20minister%20of%20state%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Housing%20and%20Urban%20Affairs%20said%20that%20PMAY-U%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdemand%20driven%20scheme%20and%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20not%20fixed%20any%20target%20for%20construction%20of%20houses.%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpmay-u-66-percent-houses-completed-lok-sabha%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bihar%20Caste%20Survey%3A%20The%20Who%E2%80%99s%20Who%20in%20the%20Data%20%7C%20Dabgar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F11160614%2FScreenshot-2023-12-11-at-4.05.27%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBeyond%20politics%2C%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20is%20a%20revolutionary%20document.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20public%20document%2C%20the%20first%20ever%20after%201931%2C%20allowing%20for%20people%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20go%20down%20to%20the%20wire%2C%20on%20what%20each%20of%20the%20numbers%20unveiled%20mean.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWho%20are%20the%20people%20referred%20to%20by%20percentages%20in%20the%20survey%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EToday%20we%20look%20at%20Dabgar%20(7%2C756%20people)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20Indian%20society%2C%20occupations%20have%20been%20assigned%20names%20of%20castes.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20ruling%20classes%20of%20this%20society%20created%20castes%20to%20suit%20the%20kind%20of%20service%20they%20required.%20The%20system%20has%20been%20designed%20and%20concocted%20step%20by%20step.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98untouchable%E2%80%99%20castes%20currently%20referred%20to%20as%20Scheduled%20Castes%20in%20the%20constitution%20were%20required%20to%20provide%20services%20which%20have%20been%20considered%20extremely%20repulsive.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20are%20some%20caste%20groups%20in%20this%20grouping%20who%20are%20not%20involved%20in%20activities%20considered%20disgusting%2C%20and%20yet%20they%20had%20been%20categorised%20as%20%E2%80%98untouchable%E2%80%99.%20One%20such%20caste%20is%20Dabgar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20438px)%2085vw%2C%20438px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22438%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22627%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDabgars%20have%20a%20minuscule%20population%20in%20Bihar.%20According%20to%20the%20Caste%20Based%20Census%20Report%202022%20released%20by%20the%20Bihar%20government%2C%20their%20number%20is%20only%207%2C756%20and%20they%20are%20ranked%20ninth%20in%20the%20list%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes.%20According%20to%20a%20socio%20economic%20report%20of%20caste-based%20enumeration%20presented%20by%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20in%20the%20Bihar%20legislative%20assembly%20on%20October%207%2C%202023%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Dabgar%20caste%20are%20the%20richest%20among%20all%20the%2022%20castes%20included%20in%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20report%2C%20families%20whose%20monthly%20income%20is%20Rs%206%2C000%20or%20less%20have%20been%20categorised%20as%20%E2%80%98poor%E2%80%99.%20On%20this%20basis%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20found%20that%20the%20poorest%20of%20the%20poor%20among%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20of%20the%20state%20are%20the%20people%20of%20Musahar%20caste%2C%20of%20whom%2C%2054.46%25%20families%20have%20a%20monthly%20income%20of%20less%20than%20Rs%206%2C000.%20Next%20are%20the%20people%20of%20Bhuiyan%20caste%2C%20who%20are%20equivalent%20to%20the%20Musahar%20caste%20at%20the%20social%20level.%20According%20to%20the%20report%2C%2053.55%25%20Bhuiyan%20families%20are%20poor.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20percentage%20of%20poor%20families%20of%20the%20Dabgar%20caste%20group%20is%20less%20than%20the%20percentage%20of%20poor%20families%20of%20Pasi%20caste%20(38.14%25).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20Dabgar%20is%20not%20a%20caste%20native%20to%20Bihar.%20Its%20people%20originally%20hailed%20from%20Rajasthan%20and%20made%20special%20kind%20of%20vessels%20to%20be%20used%20as%20spoons%20and%20ladles.%20They%20used%20wood%20and%20iron%20to%20make%20the%20utensils.%20Since%20spoons%20are%20pressed%20to%20give%20them%20a%20sunken%20shape%2C%20their%20makers%20were%20called%20%3Cem%3Edabgar%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWomen%20of%20this%20caste%20used%20to%20make%20earthen%20stoves%2C%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echulhas%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20houses%20of%20people%20of%20other%20castes%2C%20while%20men%20made%20flasks%2C%20ladles%20and%20other%20types%20of%20spoons.%20Due%20to%20the%20nature%20of%20their%20work%2C%20this%20caste%20group%20came%20to%20be%20regarded%20differently%20from%20other%20Scheduled%20Castes.%20However%2C%20even%20the%20necessity%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Echulha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E-making%20did%20not%20ensure%20that%20the%20women%20of%20this%20caste%20could%20enter%20the%20houses%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20castes.%20They%20made%20stoves%20outside%20their%20homes%20and%20when%20the%20stove%20was%20ready%2C%20they%20were%20handed%20grains%2C%20etc.%20as%20wages.%20Once%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Echulha%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewas%20ready%2C%20a%20purification%20ritual%20was%20carried%20out%20after%20which%20the%20stoves%20made%20by%20the%20Dabgars%20were%20taken%20inside%20the%20house%20and%20placed%20in%20the%20kitchen.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20present%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Dabgar%20caste%20are%20engaged%20in%20making%20neither%20spoons%20nor%20stoves%2C%20except%20during%20the%20Chhath%20festival.%20Because%20they%20made%20funnels%2C%20they%20also%20came%20in%20touch%20with%20people%20of%20the%20Teli%20caste.%20The%20people%20of%20the%20Dabgar%20caste%20eventually%20took%20to%20farming%20and%20other%20occupations.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fact%20is%20that%20the%20progress%20of%20any%20caste%20depends%20on%20the%20nature%20of%20its%20relationship%20with%20prosperous%20castes.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20biggest%20reason%20behind%20the%20poor%20condition%20of%20Musahar%20families%20is%20that%20they%20have%20been%20kept%20distant%20from%20the%20affluent%20castes.%20The%20people%20of%20the%20Dom%20caste%20only%20cross%20paths%20with%20the%20people%20of%20affluent%20castes%20at%20cremation%20grounds%20or%20while%20cleaning%20dirty%20drains.%20In%20Bihar%2C%2053.10%25%20Dom%20families%20live%20on%20an%20income%20of%20less%20than%20Rs%206%2C000%20per%20month.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Moreover%2C%20for%20a%20caste%20whose%20total%20population%20is%20less%20than%208%2C000%2C%20individual%20affluence%20does%20not%20matter%20much.%20The%20truth%20is%20that%20this%20caste%20is%20included%20among%20the%20castes%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20extinction.%20Had%20the%20cause%20of%20extinction%20been%20the%20eradication%20of%20the%20concept%20of%20caste%2C%20it%20would%20be%20a%20different%20matter%2C%20but%20that%20is%20not%20the%20case.%20Most%20of%20the%20people%20of%20this%20caste%20have%20now%20stopped%20calling%20themselves%20Dabgar%20and%20have%20merged%20themselves%20with%20other%20castes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerhaps%20it%20is%20only%20due%20to%20caste%20reservation%20that%207%2C756%20people%20in%20Bihar%20still%20believe%20that%20they%20belong%20to%20the%20Dabgar%20caste.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F261396%2Fbihar-caste-survey-dabgar-caste-society%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20earlier%20parts%20of%20the%20series%20on%20the%20following%20communities%20by%20clicking%20on%20their%20names%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%5C%22%3EGhasi%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3ESantrash%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3EMadaria%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-koeri-kushwaha%5C%22%3EKoeri%2FKushwaha%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-chaupal%5C%22%3EChaupal%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-nai-hajjaam%5C%22%3ENai%2FHajjaam%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-pasi%5C%22%3EPasi%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-