Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fin-jammu-and-kashmir-all-eyes-are-on-the-supreme-court-today%5C%22%3EIn%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Verdict%2C%20the%20SC%20Has%20Done%20What%20Many%20Locals%20Had%20Feared%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20chief%20minister%2C%20Omar%20Abdullah%20also%20alleged%20that%20he%20was%20put%20under%20house%20arrest%20on%20Monday%20morning%20ahead%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20live%20broadcast%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20Omar%20said%20that%20the%20main%20gate%20of%20his%20Srinagar%20home%20had%20been%20locked%20and%20he%20was%20prevented%20from%20speaking%20to%20the%20media.%20Media%20persons%20were%20turned%20away%20by%20authorities%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20knocked%20on%20the%20doors%20of%20SC%20with%20the%20hope%20of%20justice.%20I%20respect%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20decision.%20We%20may%20have%20failed%2C%20the%20decision%20may%20be%20disappointing%2C%20but%20it%20is%20a%20temporary%20setback.%20Ours%20is%20a%20political%20fight%20and%20we%20will%20fight%20it%20within%20the%20ambit%20of%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20succeeded%20in%20achieving%20its%20political%20objective%20after%2070%20years.%20We%20too%20will%20continue%20to%20strive%20politically%20so%20that%20whatever%20was%20snatched%20from%20us%20on%20August%205%2C%202019%20is%20given%20back.%20Whether%20it%20is%20possible%20to%20again%20knock%20on%20the%20door%20of%20the%20court%20will%20be%20decided%20after%20our%20lawyers%20go%20into%20the%20details%20of%20the%20verdict.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20observations%20on%20the%20restoration%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20statehood%20and%20the%20direction%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20on%20holding%20assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20union%20territory%20by%20September%20next%20year%2C%20Abdullah%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CElection%20is%20not%20a%20pressing%20issue%20and%20statehood%20also%20is%20not%20an%20important%20issue%20for%20us.%20We%20were%20not%20expecting%20a%20verdict%20like%20this%20but%20maybe%20we%20will%20succeed%20next%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20address%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20rejected%20the%20%E2%80%98house%20arrest%E2%80%99%20claims%20of%20Mufti%20and%20Abdullah%2C%20terming%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9Ctotally%20baseless%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20has%20been%20put%20under%20house%20arrest%20or%20arrested%20due%20to%20political%20reasons.%20It%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20spread%20rumours%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20in%20Srinagar%20district%2C%20which%20is%20home%20to%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20top%20political%20leadership%2C%20also%20claimed%20that%20no%20one%20was%20under%20house%20arrest.%20However%2C%20media%20persons%20were%20turned%20away%20from%20Gupkar%20Road%2C%20where%20Abdullah%20lives%20along%20with%20his%20father%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Farooq%20Abdullah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F30042256%2FScreenshot-2020-07-30-at-4.20.52-AM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221073%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F30042256%2FScreenshot-2020-07-30-at-4.20.52-AM.png%201073w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F30042256%2FScreenshot-2020-07-30-at-4.20.52-AM-268x300.png%20268w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F30042256%2FScreenshot-2020-07-30-at-4.20.52-AM-916x1024.png%20916w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-469956%5C%22%20hei